# Registrar o crear un usuari
POST http://localhost:8080/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test2",
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "phone": "1234",
  "registration_date": "2026-01-02",
  "password": "password"
}

### Iniciar sessió amb un usuari autenticat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login 
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### Iniciar sessió de manera inválida
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "bad_password"
}

### Obtindre els usuaris existents
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/index
Accept: application/json
### Obtindre un usuari existent
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/show/1
Accept: application/json

### Actualitzar un usuari correctament
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/update/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Juan Actualizado",
    "email": "nuevo_email@test.com",
    "phone": "555-1234",
    "registration_date": "2023-01-01"
}


### Eliminar un usuari existent
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/destroy/1
Accept: application/json